und: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 6;"><td rowspan="3" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4.</span></p></td><td rowspan="3" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Olimpiya va Paralimpiya oʻyinlariga tayyorgarlik koʻrayotgan sport turlari boʻyicha milliy terma jamoalarning tarkiblarini shakllantirish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalarning asosiy va zaxira tarkiblari hamda trener, shifokor va boshqa sport mutaxassislari tarkibini tasdiqlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025 — 2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td rowspan="3" style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td rowspan="3" style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">sport federatsiyalari</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(uyushmalari)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 7;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Olimpiya oʻyinlarida ishtirok etish uchun Oʻzbekiston sport delegatsiyasi tarkibini shakllantirish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2028-yil iyul</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 8;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Paralimpiya oʻyinlarida ishtirok etish uchun Oʻzbekiston sport delegatsiyasi tarkibini shakllantirish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2028-yil sentabr</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 9;"><td rowspan="4" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">5.</span></p></td><td rowspan="4" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Olimpiya oʻyinlariga Oʻzbekiston sportchilari zaxirasini kengaytirish maqsadida iqtidorli sportchilarni eng quyi boʻgʻindan boshlab saralash va ularni professional tayyorlash tizimini yoʻlga qoʻyish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Olimpiya sport turlari boʻyicha oʻsmirlar va yoshlar oʻrtasidagi Oʻzbekiston chempionatlarini uch bosqichli “Yangi Oʻzbekiston Olimpiya choʻqqilari” sport musobaqalari shaklida oʻtkazib borish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. “Yangi Oʻzbekiston Olimpiya choʻqqilari” sport musobaqalarining mintaqaviy va hududiy (birinchi va ikkinchi) bosqichlarini yuqori saviyada tashkil etish va oʻtkazish hamda gʻolib va sovrindorlarni ragʻbatlantirib borish.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yildan boshlab doimiy</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport va ommaviy jismoniy tarbiya tadbirlarining respublika va hududiy kalendar rejalari doirasidagi mablagʻlar, ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Qoraqalpogʻiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Kengashi, Toshkent shahri, viloyatlar va tuman (shahar) hokimliklari,</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">sport federatsiyalari</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(uyushmalari)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 10;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. “Yangi Oʻzbekiston Olimpiya choʻqqilari” sport musobaqalarining respublika final (uchinchi) bosqichini Olimpiya shaharchasida “Prezident Olimpiadasi” sifatida oʻtkazish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4. “Yangi Oʻzbekiston Olimpiya choʻqqilari” sport musobaqalarining respublika final bosqichida saralangan sportchilarni quyidagi sport taʼlim muassasalariga milliy terma jamoalarning zaxirasi sifatida tayyorlash uchun yoʻnaltirib borish:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">birinchi va ikkinchi oʻrinlarni qoʻlga kiritgan sportchilar — Respublika Olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markaziga;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">uchinchi oʻrinni qoʻlga kiritgan sportchilar — hududiy olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazlariga.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">5. “Yangi Oʻzbekiston Olimpiya choʻqqilari” sport musobaqalarida saralangan ikkinchi va uchinchi oʻrinlarni qoʻlga kiritgan sportchilar oʻrtasida qoʻshma oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlarini hamda nazorat bellashuvlarini oʻtkazib borish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">sport federatsiyalari</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(uyushmalari)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 11;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">6. Olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazlari hamda oliy sport va sport turlari boʻyicha mahorat maktablariga qabul qilingan oʻquvchi-sportchi tomonidan qoʻlga kiritilgan sport natijalari uchun belgilanadigan ustamaning 10 foiz qismini uni sport maktabida tayyorlagan trenerga toʻlab borishni nazarda tutuvchi Hukumat qarori loyihasini Vazirlar Mahkamasiga kiritish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil noyabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 12;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">7. Sport vazirligi tizimidagi 56 ta ixtisoslashtirilgan sport maktablari faoliyatini takomillashtirish boʻyicha normativ-huquqiy hujjat loyihasini ishlab chiqish va Vazirlar Mahkamasiga kiritish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2026-yil iyun</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;"> </span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 13;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">6.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Nodavlat jismoniy tarbiya-sport tashkilotlari, shu jumladan, xususiy sport klublari faoliyatini tartibga solish va yanada rivojlantirish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Nodavlat jismoniy tarbiya-sport tashkilotlari, shu jumladan, xususiy sport klublari faoliyatini tartibga solish. Bunda quyidagilarni nazarda tutuvchi Hukumat qarori loyihasini ishlab chiqish va Vazirlar Mahkamasiga kiritish:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">jismoniy tarbiya-sport tashkilotlari reyestrini shakllantirish, yuritish va reyestrdan chiqarish;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">jismoniy tarbiya-sport tashkilotlari faoliyati uchun sportchi tayyorlash boʻyicha minimal talab va shartlarni belgilash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil noyabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oliy taʼlim, fan va innovatsiyalar vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">K. Sharipov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Maktabgacha va maktab taʼlimi vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">X. Umarova</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 14;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Har 10 ta mahallada kamida 1 ta zamonaviy xususiy sport klubi faoliyatini yoʻlga qoʻyish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil dekabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Qoraqalpogʻiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Kengashi, viloyatlar va Toshkent shahri hokimliklari</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 15;"><td style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">7.</span></p></td><td style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport va ommaviy jismoniy tarbiya tadbirlarining kalendar rejasiga muvofiq milliy terma jamoalarning kompleks va xalqaro nufuzli musobaqalarga tayyorgarlik koʻrishi hamda ushbu musobaqalarda ishtirok etishini tashkil etish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalar uchun aniq maqsad va natijadorlikka yoʻnaltirilgan respublika va xorijda uzluksiz oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlarini tashkil etish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Kompleks va xalqaro nufuzli musobaqalarga tayyorgarlik koʻradigan va ishtirok etadigan milliy terma jamoalarni doimiy tarzda maxsus sport ekipirovkalari va sport inventarlari bilan taʼminlab borish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Kompleks va xalqaro nufuzli musobaqalarga tayyorgarlik koʻrishni tashkil etish hamda milliy terma jamoalarning ushbu musobaqalarda ishtirokini taʼminlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025 — 2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Davlat budjetidan ajratiladigan mablagʻlar, ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">sport federatsiyalari</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(uyushmalari)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 16;"><td rowspan="3" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">8.</span></p></td><td rowspan="3" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2026-yil Aichi va Nagoya shahrida (Yaponiya) boʻlib oʻtadigan Osiyo va Paraosiyo oʻyinlariga tayyorgarlik koʻrish va milliy terma jamoalarning muvaffaqiyatli ishtirokini taʼminlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalar uchun uzluksiz oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlarini oʻtkazish hamda ularning ushbu musobaqalarda ishtirok etishini taʼminlash.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Milliy terma jamoalarni doimiy tarzda maxsus sport ekipirovkalari va sport inventarlari bilan taʼminlab borish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Milliy terma jamoalarning Osiyo va Paraosiyo oʻyinlarida muvaffaqiyatli ishtirokini taʼminlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-2026-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Davlat budjetidan ajratiladigan mablagʻlar, ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">sport federatsiyalari</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(uyushmalari)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 17;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4. Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi tuzilmasida kurash milliy sportini rivojlantirish boʻyicha boʻlim faoliyatini yoʻlga qoʻyish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil iyul</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;"> </span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 18;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">5. Paralimpiya sport turlarini yanada rivojlantirish boʻyicha Oʻzbekiston Respublikasi Prezidenti qarori loyihasini ishlab chiqish va kiritish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil oktabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 19;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">9.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sportning eshkak eshish turlari boʻyicha boʻlib oʻtadigan oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlari va sport musobaqalari davrida sportchilarning xavfsizligini taʼminlashni tashkil qilish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlari va sport musobaqalarini oʻtkazishdan oldin Favqulodda vaziyatlar vazirligining hududiy boʻlinmalariga talabnoma yuborish.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Doimiy</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlari va sport musobaqalari tashkilotchilari</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 20;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlari va sport musobaqalari tashkilotchilarining talabnomalariga asosan sportchilarning xavfsizligini taʼminlash boʻyicha zarur chora-tadbirlarni amalga oshirish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Favqulodda vaziyatlar vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">B. Qudratxoʻjayev</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 21;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">10.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sportning eshkak eshish turlari boʻyicha sport bazalarining moddiy-texnika bazasini yaxshilash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Suv sporti turlari boʻyicha Respublika oliy sport mahorati maktabining Toshkent viloyati Oʻrta Chirchiq tumani Tuyaboʻgʻiz qoʻrgʻonida joylashgan eshkak eshish sport bazasini mustahkamlash.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Sportning eshkak eshish turlari boʻyicha oʻquv-yigʻin mashgʻulotlari va musobaqalarni oʻtkazib borishda masofalarni belgilash va jarayonlarni kuzatib borish imkoniyatlariga ega boʻlgan elektron kompleks tizimni Toshkent dengiziga oʻrnatish uchun xarid qilish va Suv sporti turlari boʻyicha Respublika oliy sport mahorati maktabi balansiga oʻtkazib berish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-2026-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasiga Davlat budjetidan 2025-yilda qoʻshimcha ajratilgan mablagʻlar</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 22;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Suv sporti turlari boʻyicha Respublika oliy sport mahorati maktabining “Qaldirgʻoch” sport bazasini davlat-xususiy sheriklik shartlari asosida rekonstruksiya qilish (zarur bino-inshootlarni qurish).</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4. Suv sporti turlari boʻyicha Respublika oliy sport mahorati maktabining Toshkent viloyati Boʻstonliq tumani Qoronkoʻl qishlogʻida joylashgan eshkak eshish sport bazasi hududida davlat-xususiy sheriklik shartlari asosida zarur bino va inshootlarni qurish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2027-2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Tashabbuskorlar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 23;"><td style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">11.</span></p></td><td style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Qashqadaryo viloyatida sport bilan shugʻullanish uchun qoʻshimcha imkoniyatlarni yaratish va sport infratuzilmasini kengaytirish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Davlat aktivlarini boshqarish agentligining Qashqadaryo viloyati Qarshi shahri Islom Karimov koʻchasi 2/82-uy manzilida joylashgan sport zali, maʼmuriy bino, garaj va yordamchi binolarini Qarshi shahri sport maktabi hamda Dehqonobod tumani “Beshbuloq” MFY Abu-Rayxon Beruniy koʻchasi 3-uy manzilida joylashgan sport majmuasini Dehqonobod tumani sport maktabiga topshirish-qabul qilish dalolatnomasiga asosan operativ boshqaruv huquqi asosida oʻtkazish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil avgust</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Davlat aktivlarini boshqarish agentligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ortikov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Qashqadaryo viloyati hokimligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Azimov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 24;"><td rowspan="4" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">12.</span></p></td><td rowspan="4" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazlarining moddiy-texnika bazasini, shu jumladan, sport infratuzilmasini yaxshilash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazlarining kamondan otish sport bazalarini bosqichma-bosqich zarur sport jihozlari va inventarlari bilan taʼminlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-2026-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 25;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazlarida bosqichma-bosqich 10 m masofaga oʻq otish sport bazalarini tashkil etish hamda ularni zamonaviy sport anjomlari va inventarlari bilan jihozlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2026-yil yakuniga qadar</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 26;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Respublika olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazi hududida homiylik mablagʻlari hisobiga barpo etilgan kamondan otish sport turi yozgi maydonining 2 qavatli binosini instrumental texnik tekshiruvdan oʻtkazish, tegishli hujjatlarni rasmiylashtirgan holda davlat roʻyxatidan oʻtkazish, kadastr va boshqa tegishli hujjatlarini rasmiylashtirish hamda binoni Respublika olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markaziga operativ boshqaruv huquqi asosida begʻaraz oʻtkazib berish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil sentabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Respublika olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazi mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Iqtisodiyot va moliya vazirligi huzuridagi Kadastr agentligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">F. Pulatov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Qurilish va uy-joy kommunal xoʻjaligi vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">Sh. Xidoyatov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 27;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4. Respublika olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlariga tayyorlash markazining ogʻir atletikaga ixtisoslashtirilgan sport zalini qurish-taʼmirlash ishlarini yakuniga yetkazish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2026-yil dekabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasiga Davlat budjetidan 2025-yilda qoʻshimcha ajratilgan mablagʻlar</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Toshkent shahri hokimligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">Sh. Umurzakov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 28;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">13.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Davlat sport-taʼlim muassasalari tennis kortlarining moddiy-texnika bazasini yaxshilash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Davlat sport-taʼlim muassasalarining tennis kortlarini xatlovdan oʻtkazish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil dekabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Qoraqalpogʻiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Kengashi, viloyatlar va Toshkent shahri hokimliklari,</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 29;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Xatlov natijalariga koʻra taʼmirtalab tennis kortlarini bosqichma-bosqich kapital taʼmirlash choralarini koʻrish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025 — 2027-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 30;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">14.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">“JAR” sport-sogʻlomlashtirish majmuasining sport infratuzilmasini yaxshilash, shu jumladan, mavjud sport inshootlarini rekonstruksiya qilish hamda yangi bino-inshootlarni (boks va voleybol zallari, sohil voleyboli maydoni, yotoqxona va boshqalar) barpo etish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Yangidan bino-inshootlarni barpo etish va mavjudlarini rekonstruksiya qilish boʻyicha loyiha-smeta hujjatlarini ishlab chiqish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Loyiha-smeta hujjatlariga asosan zarur mablagʻlar ajratilishini taʼminlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil oktabr</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ijtimoiy va ishlab chiqarish infratuzilmasini rivojlantirish dasturi doirasida Ichki ishlar vazirligiga ajratiladigan mablagʻlar</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ichki ishlar vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Tashpulatov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 31;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Loyiha-smeta hujjatlariga asosan yangidan bino-inshootlarni barpo etish va mavjudlarini rekonstruksiya qilish ishlarini amalga oshirish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4. Futbol boʻyicha mashgʻulotlar maydonini mukammal taʼmirlash.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">5. “JAR” sport-sogʻlomlashtirish majmuasining voleybol sport inshootlarini Oʻzbekiston voleybol federatsiyasiga begʻaraz asosda biriktirish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-2026-yillar davomida</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 32;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">15.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Milliy terma<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"> jamoalar tayyorgarlik jarayoniga zamonaviy ilmiy-uslubiy texnologiyalarni joriy qilish, shuningdek, ularni tibbiy-farmokologik jihatdan taʼminlashni tashkil qilish.</span></span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilarini musobaqalarga tayyorlash va oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlari jarayonlarini raqamlashtirish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilarining xalqaro sport musobaqalarda ishtirokini taʼminlash boʻyicha mahalliy va xorijiy mutaxassislarni (sport mutaxassislari, shifokorlar, fiziologlar, diyetologlar va boshqalar) jalb qilib borish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025 — 2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">sport federatsiyalari (uyushmalari)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 33;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Davlat sport tibbiyoti ilmiy-amaliy markazi faoliyatini tashkil qilish boʻyicha Hukumat qarori loyihasini Vazirlar Mahkamasiga kiritish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil noyabr</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 34;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">16.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Milliy terma<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;"> jamoalarni nufuzli sport musobaqalariga tayyorlashda sportchi, trener, hakam va boshqa mutaxassislar malakasini tizimli oshirib borishni yoʻlga qoʻyish.</span></span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Mahalliy va xorijiy sport mutaxassislari ishtirokida sport-taʼlim muassasalari va hududiy sport federatsiyalari (uyushmalari) trenerlari uchun joylarda reja-grafik asosida seminarlar tashkil etib borish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Jismoniy tarbiya va sport boʻyicha mutaxassislarni qayta tayyorlash va malakasini oshirish instituti bazasida reja-grafik asosida milliy terma jamoalar trenerlarining malakasini oshirish boʻyicha qisqa muddatli kurslarni tashkil etish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Olimpiya va paralimpiya sport turlari boʻyicha oʻzbekistonlik xalqaro toifadagi hakamlarning xalqaro tashkilotlar tomonidan tashkil etiladigan seminarlar va xalqaro sport musobaqalarida ishtirokini taʼminlab borish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4. Milliy terma jamoalar sport shifokorlari, psixologlari va diyetologlarining rivojlangan xorijiy davlatlarda malakasini oshirib borishini tashkil qilish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025 — 2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">sport federatsiyalari</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(uyushmalari)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 35;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">5. Oʻzbekiston davlat sport akademiyasi faoliyatini tashkil qilish boʻyicha quyidagilarni koʻzda tutuvchi Hukumat qarori loyihasini ishlab chiqish va Vazirlar mahkamasiga kiritish:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">boshqaruv, texnik, xizmat koʻrsatuvchi va oʻquv-yordamchi xodimlarning namunaviy shtatlar jadvali hamda xodimlar mehnatiga haq toʻlash tartibini tasdiqlash;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">talabalarni qabul qilish, attestatsiyadan oʻtkazish va ularning oʻqishini koʻchirish tartibini belgilash;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">professor-oʻqituvchilar tarkibining talabalarga nisbatini, shuningdek, talaba-sportchilar uchun sutkalik oziq-ovqat normalarini tasdiqlash;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Akademiya magistraturasiga oʻqishga qabul qilish, shuningdek, tayanch doktorantura va doktorantura institutlari hamda ilmiy darajalar beruvchi ilmiy kengashlar faoliyatini tashkil etish tartibini tasdiqlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2026/2027 oʻquv yiliga qadar</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">-</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 36;"><td style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">17.</span></p></td><td style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Olimpiya va Paralimpiya oʻyinlariga tayyorgarlik koʻrayotgan milliy terma jamoalar sportchilarining ijtimoiy-maishiy va moddiy taʼminotini yaxshilash boʻyicha zarur chora-tadbirlarni amalga oshirib borish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Sportchilarning yashash va tayyorgarlik koʻrish joylaridagi shart-sharoitlarni monitoring qilib borish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Sportchilarning ijtimoiy-maishiy va moddiy taʼminotini tizimli ravishda yaxshilab borish choralarini koʻrish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Sportchilarning Olimpiya va Paralimpiya oʻyinlariga tayyorgarlik koʻrishda oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlari va sport musobaqalarida uzluksiz ishtirok etib borishiga moliyaviy koʻmaklashish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025 — 2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Mahalliy budjet mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Qoraqalpogʻiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Kengashi, viloyatlar va Toshkent shahri hokimliklari,</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 37;"><td style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">18.</span></p></td><td style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Olimpiya va Paralimpiya oʻyinlariga tayyorgarlik koʻrayotgan milliy terma jamoalarining asosiy va zaxira tarkibi sportchilarini tibbiy-farmakologik jihatdan taʼminlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalarning asosiy va zaxira tarkibi sportchilarini bir yilda ikki marotaba chuqurlashtirilgan tibbiy koʻrikdan oʻtkazish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Milliy terma jamoalarning asosiy va zaxira tarkibi<br />sportchilarini mobil ekspress-laboratoriya tekshiruvlaridan oʻtkazib borishni tashkil qilish.</span><br /> </p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025 — 2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Davlat budjetidan ajratiladigan mablagʻlar, ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy paralimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">M. Tashxodjayev</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sogʻliqni saqlash vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Xudayarov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Sport vazirligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Ikramov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 38;"><td rowspan="2" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">19.</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Milliy terma jamoalar aʼzolarini dopingga qarshi kurashish jihatdan qoʻllab-quvvatlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilari haqida maʼlumotlarni toʻplash va saqlash uchun moʻljallangan “ADAMS” tizimiga sportchilar tomonidan maʼlumotlar kiritilishiga koʻmaklashish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilari, trenerlari va tibbiyot xodimlari uchun dopingga qarshi kurashish boʻyicha reja-grafik asosida seminarlar tashkil qilib borish.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Milliy terma jamoalar tibbiyot xodimlariga sportda doping qoʻllanishining oldini olish va dopingga qarshi kurashish boʻyicha nazoratni amalga oshirish borasida uslubiy yordam koʻrsatish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-2028-yillar davomida</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Davlat budjeti mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td rowspan="2" style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Milliy antidoping agentligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Sadikov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 39;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">4. Milliy antidoping agentligi tomonidan biologik namunalarni toʻplash va tadqiqotlar (doping-testlar) oʻtkazish boʻyicha maxsus moslamalar hamda boshqa tovar va xizmatlarni xarid qilish tender va tanlov savdolarini oʻtkazmasdan, maxsus axborot portalida tegishli axborotlarni joylashtirmasdan hamda xarid qilish tartib-taomillarini elektron shaklda oʻtkazmasdan toʻgʻridan-toʻgʻri shartnomalar, shu jumladan, toʻgʻridan-toʻgʻri import shartnomalari orqali amalga oshirilishini koʻzda tutuvchi normativ-huquqiy hujjat loyihasini ishlab chiqish va Hukumatga kiritish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil dekabr</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 40;"><td rowspan="3" style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">20.</span></p></td><td rowspan="3" style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilarini dopingga qarshi kurashish masalalari yuzasidan uzluksiz qoʻllab-quvvatlashni tashkil qilish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilarini dopingga qarshi kurashish masalalari yuzasidan uzluksiz qoʻllab-quvvatlash boʻyicha aloqa platformasi faoliyatini yoʻlga qoʻyish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2026-yildan boshlab</span></p></td><td rowspan="3" style="width: 13.44%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="13%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Ijrochilar va homiylar mablagʻlari</span></p></td><td rowspan="3" style="width: 17.6%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="17%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Milliy antidoping agentligi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">A. Sadikov</em>),</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Oʻzbekiston Milliy olimpiya qoʻmitasi</span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">(<em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">O. Umarov</em>)</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 41;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2. Platforma faoliyatini tashkil etish uchun autsorsing asosida xizmat koʻrsatuvchi tashkilotni tanlab olish va shartnoma tuzish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border: none; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">2025-yil noyabr</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 42;"><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">3. Platformaning uzluksiz faoliyat koʻrsatishini taʼminlash.</span></p></td><td style="width: 11.54%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-bottom-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-right-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="11%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Doimiy, 2026-yildan boshlab</span></p></td></tr><tr style="mso-yfti-irow: 43; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes;"><td style="width: 2.74%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="2%"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">21.</span></p></td><td style="width: 26.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="26%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilarini dopingga qarshi kurashish yuzasidan doimiy nazorat qilib borish.</span></p></td><td style="width: 27.96%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 2.85pt 0cm 2.85pt;" valign="top" width="27%"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 15.35pt;"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="mso-ansi-language: UZ-CYR;">1. Milliy terma jamoalar sportchilari oʻquv-mashgʻulot yigʻinlari va